    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Solid driver in fair overall condition. It runs and drives, but it shows its age with visible cosmetic wear, a used interior, and the kind of imperfections you\u2019d expect from a car that has not been restored or kept to show standards. A reasonable option for someone looking for a usable car at a more approachable price, with room to improve if desired.",
      "price": 18900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Fair-condition older vehicle priced accordingly. It shows clear signs of age and regular use, with noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, but it remains a decent, usable car for someone looking for affordable transportation. Expect imperfections in the paint and trim, some blemishes and wear inside the cabin, and an overall presentation that is respectable but not especially sharp. This is not a pristine example, but it should suit a buyer who wants a reasonably serviceable vehicle and understands it has some age-related wear.",
      "price": 16900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer who values low upfront cost and solid everyday utility. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it still offers dependable transportation value at an approachable price. A smart opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone seeking inexpensive wheels.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout that\u2019s perfect for someone after cheap wheels or a handy project. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it\u2019s a straightforward, affordable option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want something budget-friendly and you appreciate a seller who tells it like it is, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest project car with strong enthusiast potential. The engine fires up and runs, transmission engages, and the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for someone looking for a budget driver, weekend tinkering project, or parts donor with real upside. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present throughout, and it\u2019s being advertised in poor condition, but it still offers a usable powertrain foundation and a complete package that\u2019s getting harder to find at this price point. Great candidate for someone who knows their way around maintenance and wants an affordable entry point.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    }
